35
00:03:17,839 --> 00:03:19,320
If it wasn't for you this time,

36
00:03:19,320 --> 00:03:20,919
I really don't know what to do.

37
00:03:20,919 --> 00:03:21,919
Thank you so much.

38
00:03:24,224 --> 00:03:25,312
Mao Chong?

39
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:27,136
It's really you.

40
00:03:29,639 --> 00:03:31,279
Yes, it's really me.

41
00:03:31,279 --> 00:03:32,360
What are you doing here?

42
00:03:32,919 --> 00:03:34,960
Oh my god.

43
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:37,320
<i>Why is Su Yu here?</i>

44
00:03:37,880 --> 00:03:38,919
I had some free time,

45
00:03:38,919 --> 00:03:40,320
so I'm hanging out with Wu Bi and Duo.

46
00:03:40,320 --> 00:03:41,520
Wu Bi is here too?

47
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:44,080
Yes, he's queuing in the dessert shop.

48
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:46,880
<i>Wu Bi and Duo are here too.</i>

49
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:49,479
<i>They're pushing me into a dead end.</i>

50
00:03:50,176 --> 00:03:51,232
Who's this?

51
00:03:52,160 --> 00:03:55,839
She's a senior from my previous school.

52
00:03:56,639 --> 00:03:57,880
Just a senior?

53
00:03:58,880 --> 00:04:00,399
I saw you two chatting and laughing just now.

54
00:04:00,399 --> 00:04:01,408
You seemed pretty close.

55
00:04:02,119 --> 00:04:03,279
How about an introduction?

56
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:05,880
You two practically grew up together,

57
00:04:05,880 --> 00:04:07,199
and you want me to introduce you?

58
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:10,600
You two have fun, and I'll go in first.

59
00:04:12,768 --> 00:04:13,792
Aren't you going to help her?

60
00:04:14,304 --> 00:04:15,720
Ningning, are you okay?

61
00:04:17,279 --> 00:04:19,720
If you dare to tell Su Yu, I'm dead.

62
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:21,839
Don't worry, Su Yu won't tell.

63
00:04:30,760 --> 00:04:32,359
Can I have some time with her alone?

64
00:04:33,160 --> 00:04:36,140
No, no, no.

65
00:04:36,140 --> 00:04:37,959
Go ahead. I'll go to pay the bill.

66
00:04:41,880 --> 00:04:44,820
Senior, I have a buddy called Han Bokuang.

67
00:04:44,820 --> 00:04:46,839
I think you look a lot like him.

68
00:04:47,440 --> 00:04:48,544
Do you know him?

69
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,000
No, I don't.

70
00:04:55,160 --> 00:04:56,799
Senior, don't get me wrong.

71
00:04:57,440 --> 00:04:59,519
They were crooked,

72
00:04:59,519 --> 00:05:00,839
so I adjusted them for you.

73
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:11,160
Where's Su Yu? Isn't he with you?

74
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,224
Nope.

75
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:20,180
Why are you dressed like this?

76
00:05:20,180 --> 00:05:21,460
Life is too vacant?

77
00:05:21,460 --> 00:05:24,480
I'm selflessly dedicating myself
to disaster relief for others.

78
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:25,480
What do you mean?

79
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:30,208
Here, I'll tell you.

80
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:34,440
Brother Wu Bi, look.

81
00:05:35,839 --> 00:05:37,880
Who's that girl?

82
00:05:41,760 --> 00:05:43,080
You two are really something,

83
00:05:43,080 --> 00:05:44,512
I can't believe you thought of this.

84
00:05:44,512 --> 00:05:45,559
Let me tell you,

85
00:05:45,559 --> 00:05:47,419
