86
00:05:47,419 --> 00:05:49,279
Not Wu Bi, and not even Duo.

87
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:51,104
Fine.

88
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:54,160
I couldn't tell that you

89
00:05:55,160 --> 00:05:57,000
are actually a cross-dresser.

90
00:05:58,359 --> 00:05:59,380
Stop it.

91
00:05:59,380 --> 00:06:01,720
Why can't I look?

92
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:02,959
Because you're a kid.

93
00:06:04,519 --> 00:06:05,839
I'm going to change my clothes.

94
00:06:12,799 --> 00:06:14,459
Let me tell you something, it's hilarious.

95
00:06:14,459 --> 00:06:17,040
You want to tell me that you were
flirting with some girl on the street?

96
00:06:17,664 --> 00:06:18,740
How did you know?

97
00:06:18,740 --> 00:06:21,160
Because I saw it.

98
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:24,399
I saw it too.

99
00:06:27,200 --> 00:06:28,239
He's not a girl.

100
00:06:28,239 --> 00:06:29,680
That was Han Bokuang in disguise.

101
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:31,119
How about it? You couldn't tell, could you?

102
00:06:31,760 --> 00:06:32,860
I really didn't.

103
00:06:32,860 --> 00:06:34,820
Can you try to think of a better excuse?

104
00:06:34,820 --> 00:06:38,519
Exactly. Brother Han Bokuang
doesn't look like that at all.

105
00:06:40,959 --> 00:06:42,040
I'm not lying.

106
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:43,072
Su Yu.

107
00:06:43,799 --> 00:06:46,040
You see, I didn't lie to you, did I?

108
00:06:48,519 --> 00:06:49,720
Don't tell me

109
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:51,799
that he was that girl just now.

110
00:07:01,959 --> 00:07:03,760
I told you to not say anything.

111
00:07:04,679 --> 00:07:06,720
What? What girl?

112
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:07,839
What's Wu Bi talking about?

113
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:13,720
Where's the girl?

114
00:07:14,399 --> 00:07:15,679
I don't understand.

115
00:07:16,359 --> 00:07:17,640
Did you see a girl?

116
00:07:18,959 --> 00:07:20,399
Enough.

117
00:07:20,399 --> 00:07:22,080
I'm trying to protect you,

118
00:07:22,080 --> 00:07:23,799
so stop biting the hand that feeds you.

119
00:07:43,160 --> 00:07:45,600
The brother just now was so handsome.

120
00:07:48,559 --> 00:07:51,160
Enough with the puppy love.

121
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:53,160
She just gave someone a compliment.

122
00:07:53,160 --> 00:07:54,440
Why would you be so jealous?

123
00:07:58,880 --> 00:07:59,920
Isn't that right, Duo?

124
00:08:02,200 --> 00:08:03,279
You hit me,

125
00:08:03,279 --> 00:08:04,880
so I hit you back.

126
00:08:17,799 --> 00:08:19,500
You're finally back.

127
00:08:19,500 --> 00:08:21,279
You must be tired from the trip.

128
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:23,839
I made some soup, and you can drink some
to warm your stomach.

129
00:09:11,680 --> 00:09:12,768
Where's Wu?

130
00:09:14,119 --> 00:09:15,300
He went upstairs.

131
00:09:15,300 --> 00:09:17,640
- Perhaps to change his clothes.
- Okay.

132
00:09:17,640 --> 00:09:19,120
Madam, let me do it.

133
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:21,440
It's okay. I'll take it up to his room.

134
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:22,599
So he doesn't have to come down again.

135
00:09:23,280 --> 00:09:24,320
Okay.

136
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:50,119
Madam, why aren't you with Mr. Wu?

137
00:09:50,119 --> 00:09:51,679
