147
00:10:20,239 --> 00:10:21,880
go to his ex-wife's room?

148
00:10:26,799 --> 00:10:27,872
I don't think so.

149
00:10:29,919 --> 00:10:31,239
Well, today he did.

150
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:34,440
After three months away,

151
00:10:35,640 --> 00:10:37,880
the first thing he does when he comes back
isn't to change clothes,

152
00:10:39,280 --> 00:10:41,200
but to see his ex-wife.

153
00:10:43,640 --> 00:10:44,640
