154
00:10:45,679 --> 00:10:47,080
that when he was abroad,

155
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:50,520
the person he missed was not me.

156
00:10:53,400 --> 00:10:55,440
Madam, I heard

157
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:58,479
that Mr. Wu's branch company
had some financial problems.

158
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:02,080
Previously, it was all handled
by Wu Bi's mother.

159
00:11:02,640 --> 00:11:03,720
And he never

160
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:06,280
found a more suitable partner.

161
00:11:07,159 --> 00:11:10,260
Maybe it's because work isn't going well,

162
00:11:10,260 --> 00:11:11,479
