169
00:11:32,600 --> 00:11:35,880
Madam, don't think like that.

170
00:11:56,239 --> 00:11:57,880
You're still up.

171
00:12:00,928 --> 00:12:01,952
I can't sleep.

172
00:12:02,880 --> 00:12:05,259
Between the plane ride and the jet lag,

173
00:12:05,259 --> 00:12:06,320
aren't you tired?

174
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:15,560
In Wu Bi's mother's room,

175
00:12:15,560 --> 00:12:17,080
