180
00:12:31,559 --> 00:12:33,600
I've never been to her room.

181
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:34,640
You know that.

182
00:12:36,760 --> 00:12:37,760
I didn't say you took it.

183
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:42,159
Maybe Wu Bi did.

184
00:12:42,960 --> 00:12:44,640
Apart from the maid and Wu Bi,

185
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:46,559
