196
00:13:29,280 --> 00:13:30,304
I don't know.

197
00:13:31,080 --> 00:13:33,719
I heard that he's living with Su Yu,

198
00:13:34,880 --> 00:13:37,359
but I'm not sure exactly where.

199
00:13:40,799 --> 00:13:41,880
