203
00:13:52,159 --> 00:13:53,699
I can't figure it out either.

204
00:13:53,699 --> 00:13:55,719
Why didn't you tell me sooner?

205
00:13:59,559 --> 00:14:00,719
You were abroad,

206
00:14:00,719 --> 00:14:02,320
and you have o many things to deal with.

207
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:04,119
