Eighty.

214
00:14:40,520 --> 00:14:42,120
You know this Li.

215
00:14:42,120 --> 00:14:43,320
He's quite easy to talk to.

216
00:14:43,320 --> 00:14:44,799
Once I offered him 500 yuan,

217
00:14:44,799 --> 00:14:46,320
he agreed to tear down the courtyard wall.

218
00:14:46,320 --> 00:14:47,900
Look, once the wall is torn down,

219
00:14:47,900 --> 00:14:49,000
the courtyard is so spacious.

220
00:14:49,000 --> 00:14:50,048
Exactly.

221
00:14:50,048 --> 00:14:52,960
Eighty. Eighty.

222
