Eighty.

223
00:15:29,000 --> 00:15:30,080
Eighty.

224
00:15:30,640 --> 00:15:32,000
Eighty.

225
00:15:34,320 --> 00:15:35,520
This is too slow.

226
00:15:36,159 --> 00:15:39,080
Come on, you two step back, let me do it.

227
00:15:39,799 --> 00:15:40,960
What is this kid up to?

228
00:15:45,320 --> 00:15:47,799
Cool! I'm doing it too.

229
00:15:51,232 --> 00:15:52,359
Be careful.

230
00:15:52,359 --> 00:15:53,520
You should come down first.

231
00:15:53,520 --> 00:15:55,520
Uncle, you should come down. Let me do it.

232
00:15:55,520 --> 00:15:56,940
You don't know how to do this.

233
00:15:56,940 --> 00:15:58,080
I want to try.

234
00:15:58,080 --> 00:15:59,320
- Go slow, okay?
- Sure.

235
00:16:00,080 --> 00:16:01,720
Duo, it's too dangerous.

236
00:16:01,720 --> 00:16:03,400
We should go fold that and rest.

237
00:16:03,400 --> 00:16:05,080
Su, keep an eye on him.
Kid's never done this before.

238
00:16:05,080 --> 00:16:07,159
Uncle, just teach me once, and I can do it.

239
00:16:07,159 --> 00:16:08,440
Okay, let me tell you.

240
00:16:08,440 --> 00:16:10,359
These tiles have to be stacked like this.

241
