- Wu.
- You try it, come on.

242
00:16:15,168 --> 00:16:16,359
Okay.

243
00:16:16,359 --> 00:16:17,359
Is that Wu Bi up there?

244
00:16:17,359 --> 00:16:18,679
That's right.

245
00:16:18,679 --> 00:16:19,808
Seems like it.

246
00:16:21,960 --> 00:16:23,000
And who's the old man beside him?

247
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:27,280
That's my ex-husband.

248
00:16:30,440 --> 00:16:31,599
And what's the deal with that woman?

249
00:16:32,280 --> 00:16:34,200
Seems like his new wife.

250
00:16:35,200 --> 00:16:36,280
And there's a little girl.

251
00:16:37,719 --> 00:16:38,840
That woman must have brought her along.

252
00:16:41,679 --> 00:16:43,679
So why is Wu Bi here?

253
00:16:44,400 --> 00:16:45,472
I…

254
00:16:47,359 --> 00:16:48,599
